    "title": "Teaching",
    "description": "Start in the top left corner of the drawing:\n\n&quot;First, I was a young person with big dreams. As I developed, I came to increasing clarity about the path that might fulfill my dreams. I did not need to finish, I just needed to begin. An external force tried to make me triangular, but after I woke up, I was the same. No external force was capable of changing me. However, after I thought about it some more, my consciousness melted, thawed, and reformed myself into a dew. Here I am today, now telling you how I became the person I wanted to be. All you need to do it start.&quot;\n\n-- Said the teacher (black triangle bottom right) when the student finally approached with the right question. ",
